headline.main: Max Ernst, Catalytic Figure in 20th Century Art, Dies; Max Ernst, Catalytic Figure in 20th Century Art, Dies

abstract: Dies Apr 1; would have been 85 on Apr 2; biog sketch; por; 4 of his works illus (L)
snippet: Max Ernst, the Surrealist artist, who was conspicuous even before World War I for his exceptional gifts and his power to startle and provoke, died in Paris yesterday. He would have been 85 years old today.
